<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Facilities</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel three-sm">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p>“We will be the best – giving excellent compassionate care to the people of Morecambe Bay.”<br/><br/>The Queen Victoria Hospital in Morecambe is operated by University Hospitals of Morecambe Bay NHS Foundation Trust - which provides a comprehensive range of acute and support hospital services for around 350,000 people across North Lancashire and South Cumbria.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
